n\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531224\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531224\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qem1665703135824.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qem1665703135824.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qem1665703135824.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qem1665703135824\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qem1665703135824__updisocc_406939\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qem1665703135824__topic_d122846e1_d122847e1_d122848e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qem1665703135824_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qem1665703135824__codeblock_d5x_x32_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nlong updisocc (unsigned char*entity, longfrom_occ, longto_occ);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qem1665703135824__topic_d86932e1_d86933e1_d86934e1_d86935e1_d86936e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1225758e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"qem1665703135824__parml_py4_z32_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Mame of the entity. You can specify an empty string (but not zero) to denote the\n                  current entity.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">from_occ</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the first occurrence to be discarded. </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">to_occ</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the last occurrence to be discarded.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qem1665703135824__topic_d86937e1_d86938e1_d86939e1_d86940e1_d86941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1225758e100\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned by updisocc</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__1\">&gt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__2\">The sequence number of the occurrence that is\n                        current after discarding the occurrence.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__2\">No next occurrence is available. That is, the\n                        occurrence is the last occurrence or there is only one occurrence.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__1\">-1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">From_occ</var> is greater than the\n                        number of available occurrences.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__1\">-2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qem1665703135824__table_d14948e1_d14949e1_d14950e1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist or is\n                        not painted on the component.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qem1665703135824__topic_d86942e1_d86943e1_d86944e1_d86945e1_d86946e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1225758e174\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qem1665703135824__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qem1665703135824__topic_d86947e1_d86948e1_d86949e1_d86950e1_d86951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1225758e187\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qem1665703135824__p_d122870e1_d122871e1_d122872e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">updisocc</code> removes one or more\n            occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> from the component and the hitlist, without\n            marking them for deletion. The argument <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> is the name of the\n            entity whose occurrences are to be discarded. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> is an empty\n            string, the current entity is used.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qem1665703135824__note_N1010C_N100F0_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> In contrast with the other\n            occurrence-handling functions, you cannot specify a value of zero for\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var>. To denote the current entity, you must pass an empty\n            string.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qem1665703135824__p_d122873e1_d122874e1_d122875e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">updisocc</code> is equivalent to the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">discard</span> ProcScript statement, where you can find more information\n            about the rules for discarding occurrences and the exact interpretation of the\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">from_occ</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">to_occ</var> parameters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qem1665703135824__p_d122876e1_d122877e1_d122878e1\">Just like <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">discard</span>, this function alters the values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curhits</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dbocc</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following C code uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">updisocc</code> in a loop to delete\n            all occurrences, thereby simulating the <code class=\"ph codeph\">clear/e</code> ProcScript\n            statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Note that, in contrast with <code class=\"ph codeph\">updelocc</code>,\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">updisocc</code> does provide a different return code when the last\n            occurrence has been processed. Otherwise this loop would not have been possible.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qem1665703135824_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qem1665703135824__codeblock_qnp_hj2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT void CLEAR_ENTITY ()\n{\nlong ret;\n\nfor ( ;; )\n{\nret = updisocc(\"\", 1, 1);\nif ( ret &lt;= 0 )\nbreak;\n}\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Because <code class=\"ph codeph\">updisocc</code> can delete a range of occurrences, one\n            might be tempted to delete all occurrences in one statement instead of with the above\n            loop, as shown below. However, the following does not work, even if the documentation\n            might suggest that it should.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qem1665703135824_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qem1665703135824__codeblock_hkr_jj2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT void CLEAR_ENTITY ()\n{\nupdisocc(\"\", 1, -1); /* This does NOT work !!! */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryi1665703135669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upaddocc</a><p>Create an empty occurrence of an entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crd1665703135753.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>updelocc</a><p>Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hor1665703135893.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upsetocc</a><p>Make the specified occurrence current.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531224\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531224\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "updisocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> long updisocc (unsigned char*entity, longfrom_occ, longto_occ); Copy Parameters entity Mame of the entity. You can specify an empty string (but not zero) to denote the current entity. from_occ Sequence number of the first occurrence to be discarded. to_occ Sequence number of the last occurrence to be discarded. Return Values Table 1. Values Returned by updisocc Value Meaning >0 The sequence number of the occurrence that is current after discarding the occurrence. 0 No next occurrence is available. That is, the occurrence is the last occurrence or there is only one occurrence. -1 From_occ is greater than the number of available occurrences. -2 Entity does not exist or is not painted on the component. Use Library: yrtl Description updisocc removes one or more occurrences of entity from the component and the hitlist, without marking them for deletion. The argument entity is the name of the entity whose occurrences are to be discarded. If entity is an empty string, the current entity is used. Note: In contrast with the other occurrence-handling functions, you cannot specify a value of zero for entity . To denote the current entity, you must pass an empty string. updisocc is equivalent to the discard ProcScript statement, where you can find more information about the rules for discarding occurrences and the exact interpretation of the from_occ and to_occ parameters. Just like discard , this function alters the values of $hits , $curhits , $curocc , $dbocc , and $totdbocc The following C code uses updisocc in a loop to delete all occurrences, thereby simulating the clear/e ProcScript statement. Note that, in contrast with updelocc , updisocc does provide a different return code when the last occurrence has been processed. Otherwise this loop would not have been possible. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void CLEAR_ENTITY () { long ret; for ( ;; ) { ret = updisocc(\"\", 1, 1); if ( ret <= 0 ) break; } } Copy Because updisocc can delete a range of occurrences, one might be tempted to delete all occurrences in one statement instead of with the above loop, as shown below. However, the following does not work, even if the documentation might suggest that it should. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void CLEAR_ENTITY () { updisocc(\"\", 1, -1); /* This does NOT work !!! */ } Copy Related Links upaddocc Create an empty occurrence of an entity. updelocc Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist. upsetocc Make the specified occurrence current. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}